POST-INSTALL:

		* Update your lilo config /etc/lilo.conf like this:

		install=/boot/boot-bmp.b
		bitmap=/boot/debian-bootscreen-woody.rle.bmp
		bmp-colors=1,,0,2,,0
		bmp-table=120p,173p,1,15,17
		bmp-timer=254p,432p,1,0,0

		Of course, you can choose any 'bmp' image in the /boot
		directory instead of 'debian-bootscreen-woody.rle.bmp'
		from the above example.
